    "code": "012", 
    "data": "1. It is highly desirable in every salaat after salaam, recite the following without talking to any one or doing anything and remaining in the same position.\nاَسْتَغْفِرُ اللهَ الَّذِیْ \nASTAGHFERUL LAAHAL LAZEE \nI seek pardon and protection from Allah Who is \nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ هُوَ الْحَىُّ الْقَيُّوْمُ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAA HOWAL HAYYUL QAYYOOMO \n“There is no god save He, the Eternal and Self-subsisting, \nذُوْ الْجَلاَلِ وَ اْلاِکْرَامِ \nZUL JALAALE WAL IKRAAME \nthe Owner of glory and generosity” \nلِجَمِيْعِ ظُلْمِیْ وَ جُرْمِیْ وَ اِسْرَافِیْ عَلٰی نَفْسِیْ وَ اَتُوْبُ اِلَيْهِ.\nLEJAMEE-E’ ZULMEE WA JURMEE WA ISRAAFEE A’LAA NAFSEE WA ATOOBO ELAYHE.\nwith reference to all my injustices, crimes and transgressions which I have committed; and I turn repentant unto Him.\n1a.\nرَبِّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَ اَهْلِ بَيْتِهٖ.\nRABBE SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AHLE BAYTEHEE.\nO Lord, send blessings on Mohammed and on his Ahlul Bayt.\n2.       Recite tasbih of Hazrat Faatemah Zahra (s.a.). It is recited after every salaat.\nاَللهُ اَکْبَرُ\nALLAAHO AKBAR\nAllah is the greatest.\n34 times\nاَلْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ\nALHAMDO LIL LAAHE\nPraise be to Allah.\n33 times\nسُبْحَانَ اللهِ\nSUBHAANAL LAAHE\nGlory be to Allah.\n33 times\nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ\nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO\nThere is no god save Allah.\nOnce\n3.       Recite:\nسُبْحَانَ اللهِ وَ الْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ \nSUBHAANAL LAAHE WAL HAMDO LIL LAAHE \nGlory be to Allah. Praise be to Allah. \nوَ لاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ وَ اللهُ اَکْبَرُ \nWA LAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAL LAAHO AKBARO \nThere is no god save Allah. Allah is the greatest. \nوَ لاَ حَوْلَ وَ لاَ قُوَّةَ اِلاَّ بِاللهِ الْعَلِیِّ الْعَظِيْمِ.\nWA LAA HAWLA WA LAA QUWWATA ILLAA BILLAAHIL A’LIYYIL A’ZEEME.\nThere is no stratagem and no power save with Allah, the Supreme Almighty.\n4.       Recite:\nمَا شَآءَ اللهُ كَانَ وَ لاَ حَوْلَ وَ لاَ قُوَّةَ اِلاَّ بِاللهِ الْعَلِىِّ الْعَظِيْمِ.\nMAA SHAA ALLAAHO KAANA WA LAA HAWLA WA LAA QUWWATA ILLAA BILLAAHIL A’LEE-IL A’ZEEME.\nThat which Allah wills takes place. There is no stratagem and no power save with Allah, the Supreme Almighty.\n5.       Say 70 times keeping the right hand on the chest:\nيَا فَتَّاحُ\nYA FATTAAHO\nO Opener.\n6.       Recite:\nلاَ حَوْلَ وَ لاَ قُوَّةَ اِلاَّ بِاللهِ \nLAA HAWLA WA LAA QUWWATA ILLAA BILLAAHE \nThere is no power nor strength (with any) save with Allah. \nتَوَكَلْتُ عَلَی الْحَىِّ الْقَيُّوْمِ الَّذِیْ لاَ يَمُوْتُ \nTAWAKKALTO A’LAL HAYY-IL QAYYOOMIL LAZEE LAA YAMOOTO \nI depend upon the everliving self-subsisting (Lord) who does not die. \nوَ الْحَمْدُ لِلّٰهِ الَّذِیْ لَمْ يَتَّخِذْ وَلَدًا \nWAL HAMDO LILLAAHIL LAZEE LAM YATTAKHIZ WALADAN \nPraise be to Allah who has not taken (unto Himself) a son, \nوَّ لَمْ يَکُنْ لَّهٗ شَرِيْكٌ فِیْ الْمُلْكِ \nWA LAM YAKUL LAHU SHAREEKUN FIL MULKE \nneither He has any partner in the kingdom, \nوَ لَمْ يَکُنْ لَّهٗ وَلِیٌّ مِّنَ الذُّلِّ وَ كَبِّرْهُ تَکْبِيْرًا \nWA LAM YAKUL LAHU WALEE-UM MENAZ ZULLE WA KABBIRHO TAKBEERAN \nnor has He any helper out of humility; and proclaim His greatness by extolling (His glory). \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَعُوْذُ بِكَ مِنَ الْبُؤْسِ وَ الْفَقْرِ \nALLAAHUMMA INNEE AO’OZO BEKA MENAL BO’SE WAL FAQRE \nO Allah, verily I take refuge with You from distress, grief, \nوَ مِنْ غَلَبَةِ الدَّيْنِ وَ السُّقْمِ \nWA MIN GHALABATID DAYNE WAS SUQME \nburden of debt and bad health. \nوَ اَسْئَلُكَ اَنْ تُعِيْنَنِیْ عَلٰی اَدَآءِ حَقِّكَ اِلَيْكَ وَ اِلَی النَّاسِ.\nWA AS-ALOKA AN TO-E’ENANEE A’LAA ADAAE HAQQEKA ELAYKA WA ELAN NAASE.\nI beseech You to please help me in discharging my duties to You and to mankind.\n7.       Recite: (link to be given of ‘Dua to be recited after Namaz-e-Subh\t‘\n8.       Recite: (i)\nاَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ \nALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMEDIN WA AALE MOHAMMEDIN \nO Allah! Send blessings on Mohammed and the progeny of Mohammed\nوَ اهْدِنِیْ لِمَا اخْتُلِفَ فِيْهِ مِنَ الْحَقِّ بِاِذْنِكَ \nWAH-DENEE LEMAKH TOLEFA FEEHE MENAL HAQQE BE-IZNEKA \nand show me the way out of the controversial quarrel unto the truth by Your permission. \nاِنَّكَ تَهْدِیْ مَنْ تَشَآءُ اِلٰی صِرَاطٍ مُّسْتَقِيْمٍ.\nINNAKA TAHDEE MAN TASHAAA-O ELAA SERAATIM MUSTAQEEMIN.\nVerily You guide whomsoever You want unto the right path.\n(ii)\nاَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ \nALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMEDIN WA AALE MOHAMMEDENIL \nO Allah! Bless Mohammed and the children of Mohammed, \nاْلاَوْصِيَاءِ الرَّاضِيْنَ الْمَرْضِيِّيْنَ بِاَفْضَلِ صَلَوَاتِكَ \nAWSEYAAA-IR RAAZEENAL MARZIYYEENA BE-AFZALE SALAWAATEKA \nwith Your superior-most blessings, \nوَ بَارِكْ عَلَيْهِمْ بِاَفْضَلِ بَرَكَاتِكَ \nWA BAARIK A’LAIHIM BE AFZALE BARAKAATEKA \nand endow them with Your excellent endowments, \nوَ السَّلاَمُ عَلَيْهِمْ وَ عَلٰی اَرْوَاحِهِمْ \nWAS SALAAMO A’LAYHIM WA A’LAA ARWAAHEHIM \nand rest them along with their bodies \nوَ اَجْسَادِهِمْ وَ رَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهُ.\nWA AJSAADEHIM WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU.\nand souls in peace and tranquility. Mercy and blessings of Allah be on them.\n(iii)   \nاَللّٰهُمَّ اَحْيِنِىْ عَلٰى مَا اَحْيَيْتَ عَلَيْهِ عَلِىَّ بْنَ اَبِىْ طَالِبٍ \nALLAAHUMMA AHYENEE A’LAA MAA AHYAYTA A’LAYHE A’LIYYABNA ABEE TAALEBIN \nO Allah keep me alive in the same style and manner Ali ibn Abi Talib had lived \nوَ اَمِتْنِىْ عَلٰى مَا مَاتَ عَلَيْهِ عَلِىَّ بْنَ اَبِىْ طَالِبٍ عَلَيْهِ السَّلاَمُ\nWA AMITNEE A’LAA MAA MAATA A’LAYHE A’LIYYABNA ABEE TAALEBIN A’LAYHIS SALAAMO\nand make me die exactly like Ali Ibn Abi Talib had departed, peace be on him.\n(iv)    Say each of the following 100 or 10 times:\n(a)\nاَسْتَغْفِرُ اللهَ وَ اَتُوْبُ اِلَيْهِ\nASHTAGHFERUL LAAHA WA ATOOBO ELAYHE.\nI ask forgiveness of Allah and I turn repentant unto Him.\n(b)\nاَسْئَلُ اللهَ الْعَافِيَةَ\nAS-ALUL LAAHAL A’AFEYATA.\nI beseech Allah for welfare.\n(c)\nاَسْتَجِيْرُ بِاللهِ مِنَ النَّارِ.\nASTAJEERO BILLAAHE MENAN NAARE.\nI seek refuge with Allah from the fire.\n(d)\nاَسْئَلُهُ الْجَنَّةَ\nAS-ALOHUL JANNATA.\nI ask Him for the paradise.\n(e)\nاَسْئَلُ اللهَ الْحُوْرَ الْعِيْنَ\nAS ALUL LAAHAL HOORAL E’ENA\nI invoke Allah for a pious and beautiful spouse.\n(f)\nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ الْمَلِكُ الْحَقُّ الْمُبِيْنُ\nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHUL MALEKUL HAQQUL MUBEENO.\nThere is no god save Allah, the true and evident sovereign.\n(i)      Every hardship that afflicts you in this world will be made easy with the help of Allah, and He shall make light your burden on the day of judgment.\n(ii)     You will remain safe from the oppression of the tyrants.\n(iii)    Your belief in Allah shall not weaken in whatever manner Satan tries to lure you to the life of sin.\n(10)   Imam Hasan bin Ali al-Askari (a.s.) advised the faithful to pray the (following) dua’ after Farj salaat:\nRecite 4 Quls then recite this dua’:\nيَا مَالِكَ الرِّقَابِ وَ يَا هَازِمَ اْلاَحْزَابِ \nYAA MAALEKAR REQAABE WA YAA HAAZEMAL AHZAABE \nO the master of slaves, O the annihilator of armies, \nيَا مُفَتِّحَ اْلاَبْوَابِ يَا مُسَبِّبَ اْلاَسْبَابِ \nYAA MOFATTEHAL ABWAABE YA MOSABBEBAL ASBAABE \nO He who opens the doors (of opportunities), O the causer of causes, \nسَبِّبْ لَنَا... سَبَبًا لاَ نَسْتَطِيْعُ لَهٗ طَلَبًا \nSABBIB LANA… (mention desires) SABABAN LAA NASTATEE-O’ LAHU TALABAN \noriginate a basis for us… (mention desires) which we may not make serve us on our own, \nبِحَقِّ لاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ مُحَمَّدٌ رَسُوْلُ اللهِ\nBEHAQQE LAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO MOHAMMADUR RASOOLUL LAAHE \nfor the sake of - “There is no god save Allah, and Mohammed is His messenger.” – \nصَلَّی اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ اٰلِهٖ اَجْمَعِيْنَ.\nSALLAL LAAHO ALAYHE WA AALEHEE AJMA-E’ENA.\nblessings of Allah be on him and on all his children.\n(11)   Recite:\nاَصْبَحْتُ اَللّٰهُمَّ مُعْتَصِمًا بِذِمَامِكَ \nASBAHTO ALLAAHUMMA MO’TASEMAN BEZEMAAMEKAL \nI begin the day, O Allah, taking refuge under Your out of reach \nالْمَنِيْعِ الَّذِیْ لاَ يُطَاوَلُ وَ لاَ يُحَاوَلُ \nMANEE-I’L LAZEE LAA YOTAAWALO WALAA YOHAAWALO \nand safe shelter were neither can harass nor ambush (me the evil of) \nمِنْ شَرِّ کُلِّ غَاشِمٍ وَ طَارِقٍ \nMIN SHARRE KULLE GHAASHEMIN WA TAAREQIN \nany unjust persecutor or preyful assaulter, \nمِنْ سَآئِرِ مَنْ خَلَقْتَ وَ مَا خَلَقْتَ \nMIN SAAA-ERE MAN KHALAQTA WAMAA KHALAQTA \neasy to be found, among Your creation, \nمِنْ خَلْقِكَ الصَّامِتِ وَ النَّاطِقِ \nMIN KHALQEKAS SAAMETE WAN NAATEQE \nirrational tongue-tied plotters and articulate brutes seeking false pretexts \nفِیْ جُنَّةٍ مِنْ کُلِّ مَخُوْفٍ بِلِبَاسٍ سَابِغَةٍ \nFEE JUNNATIN MIN KULLE MAKHOOFIN BELEBAASIN SAABEGHATIN \nto commit crimes (against humanity). Clad in armour \nوِلآَءِ اَهْلِ بَيْتِ نَبِيِّكَ مُحْتَجِبًا مِنْ کُلِّ قَاصِدٍ لِیْ \nWELAAE AHLE BAYTE NABEEYEKA MOHTAJEBAN MIN KULLE QAASEDIN LEE\nof the love of the Ahlul Bayt of Your Prophet I have been rendered secure against evil schemes, \nاِلٰی اَذِيَّةٍ بِجِدَارٍ حَصِيْنٍ \nELAA AZIYYATIN BEJEDAARIN HASEENENIL \nwalled in and kept within the well-fortified walls erected \nاْلاِخْلاَصِ فِیْ اْلاِعْتِرَافِ \nIKHLAASE FIL E-A’TERAAFE \non the foundation of sincere heart and soul declaration of their rights\nبِحَقِّهِمْ وَ التَّمَسُّكِ بِحَبْلِهِمْ مُوْقِنًا اَنَّ الْحَقَّ لَهُمْ \nBEHAQQEHIM WAT TAMASSOKE BEHABLEHIM MOOQENAN ANNAL HAQQA LAHUM \nand inseparable attachment to their friendship, knowing for certain that truth belongs to them,\nوَ مَعَهُمْ وَ فِيْهِمْ وَ بِهِمْ اُوَالِیْ مَنْ وَالَوْا وَ اُجَانِبُ مَنْ جَانَبُوْا \nWA MA-A’HUM WA FEEHIM WA BEHIM OWAALEE MAN WAALAW WA OJAANEBO MAN JAANABOO \n(it is) along with them in them and around them. Whoso loves them is my friend; I forsake those who drift away from them; \nفَاَعِذْنِیْ اَللّٰهُمَّ بِهِمْ مِنْ شَرِّ کُلِّ مَا اَتَّقِيْهِ \nFA-AI’ZNEE ALLAAHUMMA BEHIM MIN SHARRE KULLE MAA ATTAQEEHE \nso my Allah keep me safe from every evil that threatens me, \nيَا عَظِيْمُ حَجَزْتُ اْلاَعَادِیَ عَنِّیْ بِبَدِيْعِ السَّمٰوَاتِ وَ اْلاَرْضِ \nYAA A’ZEEMO HAJAZTUL A-A’AADEYA A’NNEE BEBADEE-I’S SAMAAWAATE WAL A’RZE \nO the Almighty come between me and my enemies \nاِنَّا جَعَلْنَا مِنْ بَيْنِ اَيْدِيْهِمْ سَدًّا وَ مِنْ خَلْفِهِمْ سَدًّا \nINNAA JA-A’LNAA MIN BAYNE AYDEEHIM SADDAN WA MIN KHALFEHIM SADDAN \njust as You set up the sky and the earth, and barricade their approach unto us from all sides, \nفَاَغْشَيْنَاهُمْ فَهُمْ لاَ يُبْصِرُوْنَ.\nFA- AGHSHAYNAAHUM FAHUM LAA YUBSEROON.\nmake them swoon and faint inside the fence so that they do not know what to do.\n(12)   Recite:\nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْئَلُكَ اْلاِيْمَانَ بِكَ \nALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKAL EEMAANA BEKA \nO Allah, I beseech You to let me have faith in You, \nوَ التَّصْدِيْقَ بِنَبِيِّكَ \nWAT TASDEEKA BENABIYYEKA \nand acknowledge the truthfulness of Your Prophet; \nوَ الْعَافِيَةِ مِنْ جَمِيْعِ الْبَلآَءِ \nWAL A’AAFEYATE MIN JAMEE-I’L BALAAA-E \n(and I beseech You to keep me safe) from all misfortunes; \nوَ الشُّکْرَ عَلَی الْعَافِيَةِ \nWASH SHUKRA A’LAL A’AFEYATE \n(and let me) thank You for the welfare, \nوَ الْغِنٰی عَنْ شِرَارِ النَّاسِ.\nWAL GHENAA A’N SHERAARIN NAASE.\nand (enable me) to dispense with the evil of the people.\n(13)   Recite:\nاَللّٰهُمَّ فَاطِرَ السَّمٰوَاتِ وَ اْلاَرْضِ \nALLAHUMMA FAATERAS SAMAAWAATE WAL ARZE \nO Allah! The Creator of the heavens and the earth, \nعَالِمَ الْغَيْبِ وَ الشَّهَادَةِ \nA’ALEMAL GHAYBE WASH SHAHADATIR \nknower of the unseen and the seen, \nالرَّحْمٰنَ الرَّحِيْمَ اَعْهَدُ اِلَيْكَ فِی هٰذِهِ الدُّنْيَا \nRAHMAANAR RAHEEMA A-A’HADO ELAYKA FEE HAAZEHID DUNYAA \nthe beneficent, the merciful, I make a covenant in this world \nاَنَّكَ اَنْتَ اللهُ لاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اَنْتَ \nANNAKA ANTAL LAAHO LAA ELAAHA ILLAA ANTA \nthat verily You are Allah, there is no god save You, \nوَحْدَكَ لاَ شَرِيْكَ لَكَ \nWAHDAKA LAA SHAREEKA LAKA \none, there is no associate with You; \nوَ اَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا صَلَّی اللهُ عَلَيْهِِ وَ اٰلِهٖ \nWA ANNA MOHAMMADAN SALLAL LAAHO ALAYHE WA AALEHI \nand that Mohammed, blessings of Allah be on Him and on his children, \nعَبْدُكَ وَ رَسُوْلُكَ \nA’BDOKA WA RASOOLOKA \nis Your servant and messenger. \nاَللّٰهُمَّ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِهٖ\nALLAAHUMMA FASALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHI \nO Allah send blessings on Mohammed and on his children, \nوَ لاَ تَكِلْنِىْ اِلٰی نَفْسِیْ طَرْفَةَ عَيْنٍ اَبَدًا \nWA LAA TAKILNEE ELAA NAFSEE TARFATA A’YNIN ABADAN \nand do not ever leave me to follow my nafs (desires) even for a flash of an eye, \nوَ لاَ اِلٰی اَحَدٍ مِنْ خَلْقِكَ \nWA LAA ELAA AHADIM MIN KHALQEKA \nnor hand over me to any of Your created beings, \nفَاِنَّكَ اِنْ وَكَلْتَنِىْ اِلَيْهَا تُبَاعِدْنِیْ \nFA-INNAKA IN WAKALTANEE ELAYHAA TOBAA-I’DNEE \nbecause if You do so it will bring me \nمِنَ الْخَيْرِ وَ تُقَرِّبْنِیْ مِنَ الشَّرِّ \nMENAL KHAYRE WA TOQARRIBNEE MENASH SHARRE \nnear to evil and keep away from good. \nيَا رَبِّ لاَ اَثِقُ اِلاَّ بِرَحْمَتِكَ \nYAA RABBE LAA ASEQO ILLAA BERAHMATEKA \nO Lord! I do not put trust in anything save Your mercy. \nفَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَ اٰلِهٖ الطَّيِّبِيْنَ \nFASALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHIT TAYYEBEENA \nThen send blessings upon Muhammad and his pure progeny\nوَ اجْعَلْ لِیْ عِنْدَكَ عَهْدًا تُؤَدِيْهِ اِلَیَّ يَوْمَ الْقِيٰمَةِ \nWAJ A’L LEE I’NDAKA A’HDAN TO-ADEEHE ELAYYA YAWMAL QEYAAMATE \nSo I deposit my covenant with You to use it on the day of judgment. \nاِنَّكَ لاَ تُخْلِفُ الْمِيْعَادَ.\nINNAKA LAA TUKHLEFUL MEE-A’ADA.\nVerily You do not break promise.\n(14)   Recite the following dua’ (known as the dua’ of Imam Ja’far bin Mohammed al-Sadiq [a.s.]) 25 times.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِلْمُؤْمِنِيْنَ وَ الْمُؤْمِنَاتِ وَ الْمُسْلِمِيْنَ وَ الْمُسْلِمَاتِ.\nALLAAHUM MAGHFIR LIL-MOAMENEENA WAL MOAMENAATE WAL MUSLEMEENA WAL MUSLEMAATE.\nO Allah, forgive all believing men and believing women, and all Muslim men and Muslim women.\n(15)   Recite:\nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْئَلُكَ بِحَقِّ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ عَلَيْكَ \nALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKA BEHAQQE MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN A’LAYKA \nO Allah! I beseech You in the name of the rights, Mohammed and his children have with You, \nصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ \nSALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN \nto send blessings on Mohammed and on the children of Mohammed \nوَ اجْعَلِ النُّوْرَ فِیْ بَصَرِیْ وَ الْبَصِيْرَةَ فِیْ دِيْنِیْ \nWAJ A’LIN NOORA FEE BASAREE WAL BASEERATA FEE DEENEE \nand let me see and recognize (the truth), (let me) have deep insight of my religion, \nوَ الْيَقِيْنَ فِیْ قَلْبِیْ وَ اْلاِخْلاَصَ فِیْ عَمَلِیْ \nWAL YAQEENA FEE QALBEE WAL IKHLAASA FEE A’MALAEE \ncertainty in my heart, sincerity in my deeds, \nوَ السَّلاَمَةَ فِیْ نَفْسِیْ وَ السَّعَةَ فِیْ رِزْقِیْ \nWAS SALAAMATA FEE NAFSEE WAS SA-A’TA FEE RIZQEE \nwell-being of myself, enough livelihood, \nوَ الشُّکْرَ لَكَ اَبَدًا مَّا اَبْقَيْتَنِیْ.\nWASH SHUKRA LAKA ABADAM MAA ABQAYTANEE.\nand let me thank You always till the end of my life.\n(16)   Zayn al-Muttaqin says that the following multipurpose dua’ was brought by Jibraeel (a.s.) to the Holy Prophet (s.a.w.a.) and said:\nWhoever prays it after Fajr salaat and also keeps it on the body as ta’weez receive the following benefits:\n(i)      Protection from death by accident;\n(ii)     Exemption from the questioning by munkar and nakir in the grave;\n(iii)    Relief from the fright of abandonment and melancholy in the grave;\n(iv)    Diseases will be cured;\n(v)     Safety from oppression and exploitation;\n(vi)    The eight gates of heaven will be thrown open for those who pray this dua’.\nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ الْجَلِيْلُ الْجَبَّارُ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHUL JALEELUL JABBAARO \nThere is no god save Allah, the Glorious, the Supreme. \nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ الْعَزِيْزُ الْغَفَّارُ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHUL A’ZEEZUL GHAFFAARO \nThere is no god save Allah, the Mighty, the Oft-forgiving. \nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ الْوَاحِدُ الْقَهَّارُ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHUL WAAHEDUL QAHHAARO \nThere is no god save Allah, the One, the Dominating. \nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ وَحْدَهُ لاَ شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAHDAHU LAA SHAREEKA LAHU \nThere is no god save Allah, the Single Who has no associate, \nاِلٰهًا وَّاحِدًا وَّ نَحْنُ لَهٗ مُسْلِمُوْنَ \nELAAHAN WAAHEDAN WA NAHNO LAHU MUSLEMOONA \nthe only God, we surrender ourselves to His will. \nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ وَحْدَهُ لاَ شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAHDAHU LAA SHAREEKA LAHU \nThere is no god save Allah, the Single, Who has no associate, \nاِلٰهًا وَّاحِدًا وَ نَحْنُ لَهٗ مُخْلِصُوْنَ \nELAAHAN WAAHEDAN WA NAHNO LAHU MUKHLESOONA \nand to Him we are sincere. \nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ وَحْدَهُ لاَ شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAHDAHU LAA SHAREEKA LAHU \nThere is no god save Allah, \nاِلٰهًا وَّاحِدًا وَّ نَحْنُ لَهٗ عَابِدُوْنَ \nELAAHAN WAAHEDAN WA NAHNO LAHU A’ABEDOONA \nthe Single, Who has no associate, and we worship Him. \nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ مُحَمَّدٌ رَّسُوْلُ اللهِ \nLAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO MOHAMMADUR RASOOLUL LAAHE \nThere is no god save Allah, Mohammed is the messenger of Allah, \nعَلِیٌّ وَلِیُّ اللهِ وَ صَلَّی اللهُ عَلٰی خَيْرِ خَلْقِهٖ\nA’LIYYUN WALIYYUL LAAHE WA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAA KHAYRE KHALQEHI \nAli is the vicegerent of Allah. Blessings of Allah be on His best creation, \nوَ مَظْهَرِ لُطْفِهِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِهٖ  اَجْمَعِيْنَ \nWA MAZHARE LUTFEHI MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHI AJMA-E’ENAT \nthe manifestation of His pleasure, Mohammed, and all his pure, \nالطَّيِّبِيْنَ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ بِرَحْمَتِكَ يَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِيْنَ \nTAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA BERAHMATEKA YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN \npious and clean children, on account of Your mercy, O the most merciful. \nحَسْبُنَا اللهُ وَ نِعْمَ الْوَكِيْلُ نِعْمَ الْمَوْلٰی وَ نِعْمَ النَّصِيْرُ.\nHASBONAL LAAHO WA NE’MAL WAKEELO NE’MAL MAWLAA WA NE’MAN NASEERO.\nAllah is sufficient for us, He is the best supporter, the best master, the best helper.\n(17)   Recite surah Qadr 10 times.\n(18)   Recite surah YaaSeen.\n(19)      Recite surah Ikhlaas 100 times.", 
    "title": "Taqibaat-e-Namaz-e-Fajr"
}